of the Senate Judiciary
Committee.

18:55.201 --> 18:57.770 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's Republican Chuck Grassley
of Iowa.

18:57.803 --> 18:59.271 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
