about Judge Gorsuch today.

19:02.475 --> 19:04.143 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

19:04.176 --> 19:09.715 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY: I think they
learned that
he is willing to be a judge, and
not be a

19:09.749 --> 19:15.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
