19:25.564 --> 19:31.604 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
show if he's going to truly be a
referee within
our governmental system.

19:31.637 --> 19:40.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And he showed that very clearly
by demonstrating
that you should look at the
facts of the days,

19:40.813 --> 19:45.684 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
look at the law and be
