views out of

19:45.718 --> 19:46.886 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

19:46.919 --> 19:51.557 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think that's reinforced by
his writings
very well.

19:51.590 --> 19:56.295 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Of course, we're going to go
through this
over the next 48 hours.

19:56.328 --> 19:59.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I believe what I'm telling
you kind of
sums up what we are going to
know at the end

19:59.899 --> 20:01.567 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of 48 hours.

20:01.600 --> 20:05.738 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Senator, many
Republicans say
