Justice Scalia?

20:14.680 --> 20:16.215 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

20:16.248 --> 20:22.455 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY: Well, I think
