21:33.092 --> 21:38.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think, in regard to corporate
interests
as an example, he's been on both
sides of

21:38.430 --> 21:40.232 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

21:40.266 --> 21:45.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He doesn't have a philosophy
that is easy
to predict, except that he's
going to interpret

21:45.437 --> 21:49.875 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
