22:16.502 --> 22:24.076 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think the base of the Democrat
Party is
very strongly wanting to
demonstrate two things,

22:24.109 --> 22:29.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
