of his approach
to the law and the Constitution,
and, secondly,

22:29.682 --> 22:34.220 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
they want to make a case that
Garland should
have been approved last year.

22:34.253 --> 22:39.024 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Finally, Senator
Grassley,
