23:13.859 --> 23:15.628 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

23:15.661 --> 23:18.364 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY: I think it's
going to be
very, very difficult and it's
going to go

23:18.397 --> 23:20.432 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on for a long time.

23:20.466 --> 23:28.474 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I do think that they should
be just as
vigorous in investigating the
leak possibility

23:28.507 --> 23:34.380 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
as well, because that's where
national security
could be at risk.

23:34.413 --> 23:40.019 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And we talk all about
investigating Trump
or Trump people, but we -- I
don't hear enough

23:40.052 --> 23:48.060 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
