be found.

23:48.093 --> 23:54.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, you think the
leaks are
more important than any possible
coordination

23:54.099 --> 23:58.404 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
between the Trump campaign and
