campaign
and the Russian government.

24:28.801 --> 24:32.771 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you think,
finally, Senator,
that the FBI's statement they
don't see any

24:32.805 --> 24:38.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
