24:38.711 --> 24:40.079 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
that puts that to rest?

24:40.112 --> 24:41.880 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:41.914 --> 24:46.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY: I think that
you're going
to have to wait until the Senate
Intelligence

24:46.919 --> 24:50.656 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Committee gets done in a couple
of weeks -- they
are going to get into that --
before I can

24:50.689 --> 24:52.458 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
