24:52.491 --> 24:57.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Senator Charles
Grassley, the
chairman of the Senate Judiciary
Committee,

24:57.062 --> 24:58.030 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
