24:58.063 --> 24:59.031 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:59.064 --> 25:00.299 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY: Thank you very
much, Judy.

25:00.332 --> 25:02.968 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And back to the
