and laws of this great country.

25:57.723 --> 25:59.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL TRENT, Friend of Neil
Gorsuch: He's
very humble.

25:59.525 --> 26:05.898 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
