would listen and
sort of wait for an opportunity
to share his

26:13.705 --> 26:15.507 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
thoughts.

26:15.541 --> 26:18.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Michael Trent has
known Gorsuch
since they were freshman in high
school, and

26:18.343 --> 26:20.879 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
